io.barracks.ota.client.api

Class PackageInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.barracks.ota.client.api.PackageInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class PackageInfo
extends Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    This class encapsulates the details about an update package.
    It is a Parcelable which allows for it to be sent back and forth to the different services with the use of an Intent
